{"tid":671254,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人記得植木的法則？","createTime":"2018-05-20T03:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T10:02:50.000Z","uid":86199,"like":82,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"fe4bdcbc05e3a9e83c3f5238920ce82b8a494861","tid":671254,"uid":86199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T03:47:09.000Z","msg":"啱啱重睇完，熱血到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n神器超型<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/20/114542_9bbcf66fd11737e692fc0e5fa9e44cb2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F20%2F114542_9bbcf66fd11737e692fc0e5fa9e44cb2.png&h=86151d9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/20/114543_11d9adb9adcdc08d9f8038a67b1f60ab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F20%2F114543_11d9adb9adcdc08d9f8038a67b1f60ab.png&h=8a685acf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/20/114544_7f08ef5e3933a9c2035a750fcf658afd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F20%2F114544_7f08ef5e3933a9c2035a750fcf658afd.png&h=c4006af0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/20/114545_68f6e7d970efd8c3e2eac291275dfc31.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F20%2F114545_68f6e7d970efd8c3e2eac291275dfc31.png&h=c0a8415c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l3GTA0cmdOg&amp;list=PLaRqYjJAcvnbtLn8oF9BfwZA64iQF4Mho\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dl3GTA0cmdOg%26list%3DPLaRqYjJAcvnbtLn8oF9BfwZA64iQF4Mho&d=z7vz%2BB42COkwiY3XNLusEP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=60ba535e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.c