ike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:07:07.000Z","msg":"嗰陣睇廣東話配音 正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df348529146171ca5233443324f8649a5aaf6d6","tid":671254,"uid":86199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec7dcd2d768c5829cfec34e147182a578b8f9f2e","tid":671254,"uid":1675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:07:07.000Z","msg":"嗰陣睇廣東話配音 正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:15:44.000Z","msg":"樓上條link都係廣東話配音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7776399836f9a7f65ecf3aeb5a8f7e9c8e221f7e","tid":671254,"uid":144529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:32:43.000Z","msg":"到後面一直都用神器打人，好少用返自己能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a2ce251265ed0c4acf461cb6155b4fae698d13","tid":671254,"uid":86199,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:18:43.000Z","msg":"一星神器 鐵（くろがね）<br />\n只要自覺到自己是天界人便可以使用，因此所有天界人都能使用。可發射出巨型砲彈攻擊對手。植木的鐵是木製砲彈；羅貝多的鐵有「絕對命中」、「連續發射」等特性。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/20/161841_2941c5363124b8455b909b5e7deefcd7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F20%2F161841_2941c5363124b8455b909b5e7deefcd7.png&h=ca1b2174&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"061e10c65501fdab157939fdc8f1e4a5166313a2","tid":671254,"uid":86199,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:21:20.000Z","msg":"二星神器 威風堂堂（フード）<br />\n取得的關鍵是忍耐。手腕外型的防禦盾牌，若對象是神器、只能擋住鐵。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/20/162117_a38aeb08197137af2b86d603c6a0f565.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F20%2F162117_a38aeb08197137af2b86d603c6a0f565.png&h=f600be4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19cdc258832002123725d1012c1b7dfb0b314df6","tid":671254,"uid":86199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:23:03.000Z","msg":"三星神器 快刀亂麻（ランマ）<br />\n取得關鍵是不惑的心。能從手中放出銳利大刀，植木的大刀與地面相連。刀片型狀可自由控制。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/20/162301_6176499aa871d7440d67bddc9c785e71.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F20%2F162301_6176499aa871d7440d67bddc9c785e71.png&h=fc218ded&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2b522b8bb9cfe26a469d78be4dcb51cc2f8d9bc","tid":671254,"uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:23:31.000Z","msg":"後面神器真係太屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過都幾好睇<br />\n前面有啲鬥智feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab9202cd45fcda28e095c47b67266b84b21ba6d","tid":671254,"uid":86199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:23:52.000Z","msg":"四星神器 唯我獨尊（マッシュ）<br />\n取得的關鍵是強健的身體。出現一個會咬人的立方體大嘴。可以在空中使用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/20/162350_fdc84706fbbac100a7db9224349cd05c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F20%2F162350_fdc84706fbbac100a7db9224349cd05c.png&h=671b97d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c645781aeaa944ae2419d13cab18830bdfe9d2a7","tid":671254,"uid":101197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7776399836f9a7f65ecf3aeb5a8f7e9c8e221f7e","tid":671254,"uid":144529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:32:43.000Z","msg":"到後面一直都用神器打人，好少用返自己能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:25:49.000Z","msg":"下，後面用lv.2能力多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n植木最屈機係能力無效化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca0bd7ea120c534b1d7e5c39498adce75723cf9","tid":671254,"uid":75778,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:27:02.000Z","msg":"細個睇animax <br />\n好鬼好睇，最記得係主角最尾冇曬啲才，獎返做平常人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be040255f713b9f1a27366e22df6fe3f2f034159","tid":671254,"uid":75778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:27:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個睇animax <br />\n好鬼好睇，最記得係主角最尾冇曬啲才，做返平常人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f1a64ea707f9f876dbdfb9ea4c69632bbdfad35e","tid":671254,"uid":101197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b7fa8b489b8e3ee17280ed3b8216d753a7b0f0b","tid":671254,"uid":34973,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:03:45.000Z","msg":"第二部個地拖都好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:30:35.000Z","msg":"可惜冇動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n將纏加諸於地拖的能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3613da91526362fa710f73239107a23a307f1266","tid":671254,"uid":185935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:34:38.000Z","msg":"當年係植木同小金毛一齊睇<br />\n<br />\n好好睇"},{"pid":"e33570488077bbd2de39cd018ce7ce8dfbbd3229","tid":671254,"uid":82404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ca0bd7ea120c534b1d7e5c39498adce75723cf9","tid":671254,"uid":75778,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:27:02.000Z","msg":"細個睇animax <br />\n好鬼好睇，最記得係主角最尾冇曬啲才，獎返做平常人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:36:36.000Z","msg":"仲有再會之才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93ab68deb674cd009fe4658b91c8396c9c40a71","tid":671254,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:37:17.000Z","msg":"福地翼老師其他作品都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n乒乓告白、探地潛龍同而家套命運輪回"},{"pid":"c4b8d267c47941e332e56f5495258115a6d25541","tid":671254,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:38:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"640e134be89f78d3a4a0e1e4425a0b5dde1ab11b","tid":671254,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:47:05.000Z","msg":"循環個idea好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2cf4f4f5a6155a34fcf920f8cf9f182cccac6f8","tid":671254,"uid":86199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:48:58.000Z","msg":"五星神器 百鬼夜行（ピック）<br />\n取得關鍵是集中力。外型是根長柱子，從使用者的手臂發射而出。可以打擊或做推進器使用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/20/164854_18c759d232bbe3e5bd3fb9aa3875dc61.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F20%2F164854_18c759d232bbe3e5bd3fb9aa3875dc61.png&h=72b623e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a8cdf204fdf354bdb7d6ed9a39640b7757810a5","tid":671254,"uid":86199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:51:58.000Z","msg":"六星神器 電光石火（ライカ）<br />\n取得的關鍵是洞察能力。溜冰鞋外型，可以讓使用者以十倍速移動，但是使用中無法跳躍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/20/165156_6678c6a0f3f756af774b7b36e1b52052.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F20%2F165156_6678c6a0f3f756af774b7b36e1b52052.png&h=b8b75223&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f52eaad15cb6320045d054bd9a62f92b39e92d6","tid":671254,"uid":75778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:57:15.000Z","msg":"個setting冇記錯係咪能力者打平常人既話會隨機損失一個才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5605864388f786ab7f84a7cfc6c990730d6aa2cc","tid":671254,"uid":86199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f52eaad15cb6320045d054bd9a62f92b39e92d6","tid":671254,"uid":75778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:57:15.000Z","msg":"個setting冇記錯係咪能力者打平常人既話會隨機損失一個才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:05:09.000Z","msg":"冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f24e45ff7db8e0102d5c163a84c5873f283c8bc","tid":671254,"uid":86199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:12:29.000Z","msg":"七星神器 旅人（ガリバー）<br />\n取得的關鍵是持久。半秒鐘內、地面上會出現一個箱子補捉對手，任何在箱子內側的攻擊都徒勞無功。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/20/171137_08f9ed41cce89ca9478832692a3bd4d0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F20%2F171137_08f9ed41cce89ca9478832692a3bd4d0.png&h=e2ad2043&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72cf6cf0831e362bd0187cd56fb68bdf9cd852c7","tid":671254,"uid":86199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:24:03.000Z","msg":"八星神器 波花（なみはな）<br />\n取得的關鍵是把握。巨大鞭子外型，可靈活地彎曲至各方向，可攻擊或擾敵。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/20/172359_32d03589a62e3fcfcd3c164e73d201bd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F20%2F172359_32d03589a62e3fcfcd3c164e73d201bd.png&h=37e1b9a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"737d01c68a038a85954247c52998cc2d48f76e1c","tid":671254,"uid":160266,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:32:46.000Z","msg":"有條友係用件衫發動能力，之後植木話佢會生pink 毛，笑到gap gap聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92bc1d5edeffdb2f1bde278c3d1e446965ace49","tid":671254,"uid":86199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T09:53:27.000Z","msg":"九星神器 花鳥風月（セイクー）<br />\n取得的關鍵是平衡。是一對可讓使用者飛行的翅膀，比電光石火容易控制。如果只剩下一半也能照常飛行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/genedavinci/1382595813-2705739837.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fgenedavinci%2F1382595813-2705739837.jpg&h=8ed98d9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cddefda7d8d02a45b9c5cf3a65aded2a8567b2fe","tid":671254,"uid":29551,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T10:02:17.000Z","msg":"臨尾嗰場鳩出招用淨幾個才有啲on9<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw有無解點解得植木可以同時用多種神器<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34f7fe4b4970401ea93b33d39528ee07e4e7f19","tid":671254,"uid":14065,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"cddefda7d8d02a45b9c5cf3a65aded2a8567b2fe","tid":671254,"uid":29551,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T10:02:17.000Z","msg":"臨尾嗰場鳩出招用淨幾個才有啲on9<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw有無解點解得植木可以同時用多種神器<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T10:07:58.000Z","msg":"天界人同時用多種神器唔難"},{"pid":"910039df28eeb7fdcaa7232e7aa82e74adc3c8fc","tid":671254,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T10:15:11.000Z","msg":"啲設定都幾奇特"},{"pid":"01db6d83bdf2868537aa5545f3092781404f6667","tid":671254,"uid":18647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T10:24:17.000Z","msg":"第二部做乜爛左尾？"},{"pid":"05f42b3b6343a25e734569c4ef223a72fdbd7e30","tid":671254,"uid":86199,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T11:00:29.000Z","msg":"十星神器 魔王（まおう）<br />\n獲得的關鍵不明。魔王是無形的武器，必須透過意志力來召喚，形象根據使用者心中對「強」的概念而決定。魔王一生中只能使用六次。植木的魔王是小林老師，是透過希望拯救同伴的意志展現；而阿諾的魔王是黑公羊外形，透過他對人類的仇恨展現。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/20/190027_70134141c4acdcec82c13e3c9e0552a0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F20%2F190027_70134141c4acdcec82c13e3c9e0552a0.png&h=65f6cde8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7f6e37fc954ca7d602b524d454e382246c878c6","tid":671254,"uid":86199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e34f7fe4b4970401ea93b33d39528ee07e4e7f19","tid":671254,"uid":14065,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"cddefda7d8d02a45b9c5cf3a65aded2a8567b2fe","tid":671254,"uid":29551,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T10:02:17.000Z","msg":"臨尾嗰場鳩出招用淨幾個才有啲on9<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw有無解點解得植木可以同時用多種神器<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T10:07:58.000Z","msg":"天界人同時用多種神器唔難"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T11:02:18.000Z","msg":"好似係因為同佢本身樹木能力結合嘅結果"},{"pid":"6b6de304e1147f4f6b8ad717fe19346c463dc8d7","tid":671254,"uid":14065,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7f6e37fc954ca7d602b524d454e382246c878c6","tid":671254,"uid":86199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e34f7fe4b4970401ea93b33d39528ee07e4e7f19","tid":671254,"uid":14065,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"cddefda7d8d02a45b9c5cf3a65aded2a8567b2fe","tid":671254,"uid":29551,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T10:02:17.000Z","msg":"臨尾嗰場鳩出招用淨幾個才有啲on9<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw有無解點解得植木可以同時用多種神器<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T10:07:58.000Z","msg":"天界人同時用多種神器唔難"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T11:02:18.000Z","msg":"好似係因為同佢本身樹木能力結合嘅結果"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T11:04:55.000Z","msg":"羅拔圖呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf521c770ef07946f8a612eb2c2a43a60dce8c9f","tid":671254,"uid":86199,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6b6de304e1147f4f6b8ad717fe19346c463dc8d7","tid":671254,"uid":14065,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7f6e37fc954ca7d602b524d454e382246c878c6","tid":671254,"uid":86199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e34f7fe4b4970401ea93b33d39528ee07e4e7f19","tid":671254,"uid":14065,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201